title: 이달의소녀탐구 #153 (LOONA TV #153)
summary:
It is the MV shooting day!
0:07 -- JinSoul comments on her hairstyle: “It really seems like Jingolas” and she thinks
that Jingolas is a handsome guy.
0:14 -- She is told that the guy’s name is Legolas. (*insert: MemeSoul whuut?*)\
0:19 -- She finally understands after Lip explains it to her.
0:35 -- Lip says that she will take over the PD duties as Cho PD is away and starts
imitating her. They leave for the MV shoot
